This is the batched greedy code (and the instance generator) used 
in the submission to ASPDAC'03, last modified on 07/25/02.  
It is experimental code, not an official release, so please do 
not distribute it.  To get a brief list of parameters type 
"steiner -help" or "gen -help" after successfuly making 
the two executables.  For bug reports or questions please contact 
me at mandoiu@cs.ucsd.edu.
